Code Overview
=============

The project follows an MVC architecture pattern using Django.

Users App
---------

The `users` application handles:

- User registration
- Email account activation
- Authentication and logout
- Role management

Courses App
-----------

The `courses` application handles:

- Training themes
- Courses and lessons
- Purchases (courses and lessons)
- Lesson validation
- Certification attribution

The business logic is implemented using Django models and views,
following an object-oriented approach.
